<p>Remember to be on a show like this one just pick up your phone and call <strong><span style="color: #800000;">866-65-THINK</span></strong>.Â  The best way to improve your chances of being on the air is ask your question or make your point up front, then provide details.Â  Also call from a quite area with a good connection and speak up so you can be well heard.Â  I canât put all calls on the air but I do my best to get most of them on.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Join Us Today as we Discussâ¦</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>My thoughts on open carry</li>
<li>Thoughts on filming demonstrations and protests</li>
<li>Thoughts on passive solar heating of a work shop</li>
<li>In a <a title="libertarian" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/a-libertarian-view">libertarian</a> government who would pay for national defense</li>
<li>One family reports on the recent tornado outbreak</li>
<li><a title="Silver" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-51-options-and-reasons-to-invest-in-silver">Silver</a> or gold or both on a current bullion buy</li>
<li>Starting a business in the firearms niche</li>
<li>Thoughts on being a traveler and modern &#8220;hunter gatherer&#8221;</li>
<li>When do you retire laying hens</li>
<li>What was different about 2008 from other election years</li>
<li>Picking a financial adviser</li>
</ul>
